images.prompt: In an organic tunnel split-view illuminated by flickering oil-lamp mist, a neon brute diva emerges amidst swirling spore clouds, her form bathed in dim cyan and brown hues that evoke a vaporwave dreamscape, intricate details woven into her fierce yet surreal presence, blending futuristic cyberpunk grandeur with a soft, hazy atmosphere reminiscent of vintage digital artwork, where the interplay of glowing neon musculature and shadowy textures creates a mesmerizing sense of depth and motion, as if she’s traversing an otherworldly conduit suspended within an elusive, vapor-tinged abyss filled with delicate tendrils of mist brushing against her contours, all captured with high-detailed realism that conjures a hauntingly immersive vision of a surreal, cyber-organic realm infused with both decadence and decay, inviting viewers into a mesmerizing fusion of organic architecture and luminous chaos.
